<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Ogden</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">In 2006, approximately 63.8% of the Ogden real estate was made up of detached and semi-detached single-family homes (duplex up and down, triplex, bungalow and two storey), with the remaining 36.2% being apartments and condominiums. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Approximately 35.2% of homes were being used for rental purposes.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Ogden has a public elementary and community school, as well as a Catholic separate school.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Ogden/Lynnwood is located in Ward 9 and represented by Gian-Carlo Carra on the Calgary City Council. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Provincially, Ogden/Lynnwood is in the Calgary-Fort riding, represented by Wayne Cao and federally in the Calgary Southeast riding, represented by Jason Kenney.</p>
        </div>
